graph LR
    subgraph "Agent System (Message Bus)"
        Planner[Planner Agent<br/>planner-01]
        Coder[Coder Agent<br/>coder-01]
        Reviewer[Reviewer Agent<br/>reviewer-01]

        Bus[Message Bus<br/>Async Queue]
    end

    Planner -->|TASK| Bus
    Bus -->|TASK| Coder

    Coder -->|REQUEST| Bus
    Bus -->|REQUEST| Reviewer

    Reviewer -->|DONE/REJECT| Bus
    Bus -->|DONE/REJECT| Planner

    Planner -.->|retrieve_experience| Memory[(Memory Store)]
    Planner -.->|save_experience| Memory

    Coder -.->|execute_prompt| LLM[LLM Layer]
    Planner -.->|execute_prompt| LLM

    Reviewer -.->|score_code| QualityScorer[Quality Scorer]
    Reviewer -.->|patch_code| CodePatcher[Code Patcher]